metadata.name: By Candlelight 1
metadata.description:
This collection is dedicated to the beauty of the female body.

When we did this photo shoot, we tried very hard with the model to convey the atmosphere, the mood, the aesthetics of the naked female body.

The light from the candles stunningly emphasizes the lines and curves of the body, shows highlights on the body, as well as conveys sexuality and gorgeous natural beauty.

I am sure you feel all this when watching this collection. 


1/1

–°anon 7D | Kyiv, Ukraine | 5184x3456
